text: ALPA or Alpa may refer to: * Alpa, a formerly Swiss camera design company and manufacturer of 35 mm cameras * Air Line Pilots Association, International * Arbitrated Loop Physical Address, used in part of some computer systems, e.g. device numbering on Fibre Channel loops * Alpa, an alternate name of Alope (Ozolian Locris), an ancient city of Greece
title: ALPA
